org.itsnat.comp.table

Interface ItsNatTableHeaderCellUI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatTableHeaderCellUI
extends ItsNatUserData
    Contains visual information of a table header cell.

    This interface is similar to ItsNatListCellUI and follows a similar philosophy.

    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
    See Also:
